window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>She's a farmer. He's the Seelie king.</b></p> <p>I took her out to dinner.<br> And liked spending the evening with her.<br> So when I invited her to the Royal Court,<br> she accepted.</p> <p>But I have been lying to her.<br> And now I have to reap what I've sown.<br> For the male she calls Commander,<br> the world knows as the Summer King.</p> <p>She's a fae with barely any magic.<br> I am the king.<br> She thinks it can't work out between us.<br> And I'll do everything in my power to prove her wrong.</p> <p><i>The Royal Obsession is book one in the Fae-ted Kings series, a spicy fantasy romance with a happily ever after.</i></p>"; 
